it services stanford university ccc info page ccc campus crusade for christ at stanford university about ccc english usa ccc is the mailing list for campus crusade for christ at stanford university its main purpose is for posting announcements and other information of general interest to people subscribed to the list if you do not want to be on the list please send a letter to majordomo lists saying unsubscribe ccc you can subscribe again at any time by writing to majordomo lists subscribe ccc feel free to post to the list by sending a letter to ccc lists stanford edu to see the collection of prior postings to the list visit the ccc archives the current archive is only available to the list members using ccc to post a message to all the list members send email to ccc lists stanford edu you can subscribe to the list or change your existing subscription in the sections below subscribing to ccc subscribe to ccc by filling out the following form you will be sent email requesting confirmation to prevent others from gratuitously subscribing you this is a private list which means that the list of members is not available to non members your email address your name optional which language do you prefer to display your messages english usa would you like to receive list mail batched in a daily digest no yes ccc subscribers the subscribers list is only available to the list members enter your address and password to visit the subscribers list address password for non stanford edu address only to unsubscribe from ccc get a password reminder or change your subscription options enter your subscription email address if you leave the field blank you will be prompted for your email address ccc list run by jon832 at stanford edu rs48 at stanford edu ccc administrative interface requires authorization overview of all lists stanford edu mailing lists
